                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I produce a certificate of the pri<lb></lb>soner's former conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted April</hi>, 1840, <hi rend="italic">of stealing lead; transported for seven years</hi>)—I was present—he is the person.</p>
